"08 · START WITH THE WORKSHOP":"08 · 从工作坊开始","Experience a better way":"体验更好的","to":"与","work with AI.":"AI 协作方式。","Leave with a practical thinking process you can continue using as AI tools change.":"带走一套实用的思考流程，即使 AI 工具改变，依然能够持续使用。",
