"09 · FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS":"09 · 常见问题","Do I need technical or coding knowledge?":"需要技术或编程知识吗？","No. The workshop focuses on how you think and communicate with AI, not coding.":"不需要。工作坊聚焦如何与 AI 思考和沟通，不涉及编程。","Is this only for ChatGPT users?":"只有 ChatGPT 用户才适合吗？","No. The thinking method can be used with ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini and other conversational AI tools.":"不是。这套思考方法也适用于 Claude、Gemini 及其他对话式 AI 工具。","Is this a prompt-template class?":"这是提示模板课程吗？","No. Templates may help temporarily. The workshop develops habits you can adapt to different tools and work situations.":"不是。模板只能暂时帮助你；工作坊培养的是能适应不同工具与工作情境的习惯。","What does “Chimps FOC” mean?":"“Chimps 免费”是什么意思？","Eligible active members of the Chimpanzee Ka-Ku Society can join the workshop at no additional fee.":"符合资格的活跃 Chimpanzee Ka-Ku Society 会员无需额外付费即可参加。","Can organisations enquire for a team?":"企业可以为团队咨询吗？","Yes. Speak with CST about the appropriate delivery format for your team or department.":"可以。欢迎与 CST 讨论适合团队或部门的授课形式。","Will AI make the final decision for me?":"AI 会替我作最终决定吗？","No. AI can help you explore and review. You remain responsible for what is useful, accurate and appropriate.":"不会。AI 可以协助探索与检视，但什么是有用、准确与合适的，仍由你负责判断。",
